if i were you is a comedy advice podcast created and hosted by jewish american comedians jake hurwitz and amir blumenfeld, known for their involvement with collegehumor and their web series jake and amir. first released on may 13, 2013, new episodes are posted every monday (as well as occasional bonus thursday episodes), featuring the duo's comedic advice for listeners who have submitted questions by email. the show has appeared on the itunes podcast charts in multiple countries, reaching number 3 in the united states.